(17, '', 'กล้อง DSLR Sony a99 ii CMOS sensor 35mm. full frame', 3, 7, '', 'กล้อง DSLR SONY', '', '<p><strong>รายละเอียดและจุดเด่นหลัก ๆ ของกล้อง</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>เซนเซอร์ Exmor R &trade; CMOS 35 มม. แบบฟูลเฟรม</li>\r\n	<li>ที่มีพิกเซลที่ใช้งานจริง 42.4 MP (ประมาณ)</li>\r\n	<li>ระบบ AF ตรวจจับระยะห่างไฮบริดและการถ่ายภาพต่อเนื่องได้ถึง 12fps</li>\r\n	<li>SteadyShot&trade; INSIDE 5 แกน &mdash; ระบบป้องกันการสั่นไหวในตัวกล้องสำหรับรุ่น A-mount</li>\r\n	<li>ระบบประมวลผลภาพ BIONZ X</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>เลนส์ A-mount ของ Sony สามารถใช้ร่วมกับเลนส์ Minolta/Konica Minolta ได้</li>\r\n	<li>ประเภทเซนเซอร์</li>\r\n	<li>เซนเซอร์ Exmor R CMOS ฟูลเฟรม 35 มม. (35.9 x 24.0 มม.)</li>\r\n	<li>จำนวนพิกเซล (ที่ใช้งานจริง</li>\r\n	<li>ประมาณ 42.4 ล้านพิกเซล</li>\r\n	<li>ความไวแสง ISO (RECOMMENDED EXPOSURE INDEX)</li>\r\n	<li>ภาพนิ่ง: ISO 100-25600 (สามารถตั้งเลข ISO ตั้งแต่ ISO 50 ถึง ISO 102400 เป็นช่วง ISO แบบขยายได้), อัตโนมัติ (ISO 100-6400, เลือกขีดจำกัดล่างและขีดจำกัดบนได้), ภาพยนตร์: เทียบเท่า ISO 100-25600, AUTO (ISO 100-6400, เลือกขีดจำกัดบน/ล่างได้)</li>\r\n	<li>ระยะเวลาการใช้งานแบตเตอรี่ (ภาพนิ่ง)</li>\r\n	<li>ประมาณ 390 ภาพ (ช่องมองภาพ) /ประมาณ 490 ภาพ (จอภาพ LCD) (มาตรฐาน CIPA)25</li>\r\n	<li>ประเภทช่องมองภาพ</li>\r\n	<li>ช่องมองภาพอิเล็กทรอนิกส์ขนาด 1.3 ซม. (0.5 type), XGA OLED</li>\r\n	<li>ประเภทจอภาพ</li>\r\n	<li>TFT ชนิด 7.5 ซม. (3.0-type)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/cb/v1/jh.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '2211201317075fba177be5eb7.jpg', 109000, 0, 0, '2020-11-21 20:17:55', 0, '2020-11-26 18:23:55'),
(18, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ LIBEC TH-650HD', 4, 13, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ LIBEC', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่ายขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ LIBEC TH-650HD&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Great camera balance can be achieved due to the counterbalance feature with the built-in spring. The fluid torque system contributes to smooth operation. The TH-650HD is an ideal entry-level tripod system for home video shootings and for digital single-lens reflex camera users.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS LIBEC TH-650HD</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n			<h3>Specifications</h3>\r\n			</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Payload</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">3kg / 6.5lb</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Counterbalance</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">FIX</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Drag mode</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">FIX</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Tilt angle</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">+90&deg; / -70&deg;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Temperature range</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">-20&deg;C to +60&deg;C / -4&deg;F to +140&deg;F</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Bubble level</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">Non illuminated</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Camera plate</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">Quick release plate</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Plate attachment</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">1/4&quot; screw</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Spare screw</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">None</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">3.2kg / 7.0lb</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Height</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">70 to 150cm / 27.5 to 59.0&quot;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Ball diameter</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">65mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Section</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">2STAGE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/me/mo/49.png\" /></p>\r\n', '2211201318105fba17ba6240d.png', 7500, 0, 0, '2020-11-21 20:17:58', 0, '2020-11-26 18:34:13'),
(19, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ Libec ALX KIT Tripod and Fluid Head Kit', 4, 13, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ LIBEC', '', '<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>9 lb Load Capacity</li>\r\n	<li>75mm Ball Fluid Head with Flat Base</li>\r\n	<li>Fixed Counterbalance and Drag</li>\r\n	<li>2-Stage Tripod with Mid-Level Spreader</li>\r\n	<li>29.3 to 64.8&quot; Height Range</li>\r\n	<li>Sliding Quick Release Plate</li>\r\n	<li>Spiked Feet with Screw-Down Rubber Pads</li>\r\n	<li>Padded Carrying Case</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The ALX KIT from Libec is a tripod system comprising the 75mm bowl Libec ALX T tripod</strong>&nbsp;and the ALX H fluid head that supports loads up to 9 lb. The 3-section aluminum tripod has an operating height of 29.3 to 64.8&quot; and features a telescopic mid-level spreader for added leg rigidity. The ALX H head provides smooth pan and tilt movements, using its fixed drag and counterbalance, and includes a sliding quick release plate for camera attachment. The plate comes with a 1/4&quot;-20 screw, and a 3/8&quot;-16 screw is also provided that stores in a thread under the plate. Because the 75mm ball base of the head has a flat bottom, the head can also be used with flat base tripods or even mounted to a camera slider platform. The entire ALX KIT tripod system stores inside of an included padded carrying case.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ALX H Dual-Base Fluid Head</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compatible with both flat and ball-base hardware, the Libec ALX H Fluid Head is a versatile tripod head for video production. The ALX H base features a standard 75mm ball-base with a flattened area containing a standard 3/8&quot;-16 threaded hole for mounting to standard flat-mount hardware found on compact sliders and other grip equipment. The pan and tilt fluid-drag mechanisms are fixed-strength, as is the counterbalance. The head&#39;s construction allows for a wide +90&deg; (down)/-80&deg; (up) tilt range. Each axis can be locked down for extra stability during stationary shots. Both sides of the tripod head feature rosettes for attaching the included pan handle on the desired side. The camera connects to the included sliding snap-in plate, which by default holds a 1/4&quot;-20 screw and a guiding pin. A 3/8&quot;-16 screw is included and can be stowed underneath the camera plate when not in use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual-base head with a 75mm ball base and flat base</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tilt lock</li>\r\n	<li>Includes quick release camera plate and dual-side rosette mount pan handle</li>\r\n	<li>Rosette adapters on both sides</li>\r\n	<li>Fixed counterbalance and drag</li>\r\n	<li>Illuminated bubble level</li>\r\n	<li>ALX T Aluminum Tripod with Mid-Level Spreader (75mm Bowl)</li>\r\n	<li>Get the stability you need for your heavy cinema camera kit by using this ALX T Aluminum Tripod with Mid-Level Spreader from Libec. The ALX T can support up to 55 lb and offers a 75mm bowl fitting for holding a wide variety of heads. The standard two-stage legs have a height range of 23.5 to 59&quot;, while a telescopic mid-level spreader is available for added stability and fast setup. The tripod also has rubber feet with integrated metal spikes for working on both smooth surfaces and rough outdoor environments. Additionally, it weighs 5.5 lb.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>ALX H Dual-Base Fluid Head</p>\r\n\r\n	<table>\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Payload</td>\r\n				<td>9 lb / 4 kg</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Camera Plate</td>\r\n				<td>Sliding plate</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Sliding Range</td>\r\n				<td>1.6&quot; (+/-40 mm)</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Plate Attachment</td>\r\n				<td>1/4&quot; screw with video pin</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Screw Sliding Range</td>\r\n				<td>3&quot; / 76 mm</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Tilt Angle</td>\r\n				<td>+90&deg; / -80&deg;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Pan Angle</td>\r\n				<td>360&deg;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Counterbalance</td>\r\n				<td>Fixed</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Drag Mode</td>\r\n				<td>Fixed</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Tilt Lock</td>\r\n				<td>Yes</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Base</td>\r\n				<td>75 mm ball with 3/8&quot;-16-threaded flat base</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Leveling Bubble</td>\r\n				<td>Yes (illuminated)</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Weight</td>\r\n				<td>2.9 lb / 1.3 kg</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n\r\n	<table>\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<th colspan=\"2\"><a id=\"shipping\" name=\"shipping\"></a>Packaging Info</th>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Box Dimensions (LxWxH)</td>\r\n				<td>15.5 x 8.4 x 5.9&quot;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>ALX T Aluminum Tripod with Mid-Level Spreader (75mm Bowl)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n	<table>\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<th colspan=\"2\"><a id=\"46404\" name=\"46404\"></a>General</th>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Load Capacity</td>\r\n				<td>55 lb / 25 kg</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Head Attachment Fitting</td>\r\n				<td>75mm bowl</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Maximum Height</td>\r\n				<td>59&quot; / 150 cm</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Minimum Height</td>\r\n				<td>23.5&quot; / 60 cm</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Weight</td>\r\n				<td>5.5 lb / 2.5 kg</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n\r\n	<table>\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<th colspan=\"2\"><a id=\"45001\" name=\"45001\"></a>Legs</th>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Material</td>\r\n				<td>Aluminum</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Leg Stages/Sections</td>\r\n				<td>2/3</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Leg Lock Type</td>\r\n				<td>Twist knobs</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>Spreader</td>\r\n				<td>Mid-level</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n	