(45, '', 'ADVANCE APS HDMI TO USB3.0 CAPTURE BOX', 15, 50, '', 'Streaming Box / Facebook live', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ADVANCE APS HDMI TO USB3.0 CAPTURE BOX</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PLUG N PLAY : เสียบใช้งานได้ทันทีไม่ต้องลง Driver</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS : Windows 7 ขึ้นไป / MAC OS X / Linux / Android 5.1 ขึ้นไป</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support Software : OBS / Wirecast / ETC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HDMI Input Formats:</strong>&nbsp;480i,480p,576i,576p,720p50, 720p60,1080i50,1080i60, 1080p24/25/30/50/60</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Output Formats Resolutions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>640&times;480/720&times;480/720&times;576/ ,768&times;576/800&times;600/1024&times;768/1280&times;720/1280&times;800/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1280&times;960/1280&times;1024/1368&times;768/1440&times;900/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1600&times;1200/1680&times;1050/1920&times;1080/1920&times;1200/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>640&times;360/856&times;480/960&times;540/1024&times;576</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frame Rate: 25/29.97/30/50/59.94/60 fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ADVANCE APS HDMI TO USB3.0 CAPTURE BOX&nbsp; กันให้สะดวกยิ่งขึ้น กับกล่องแปลงสัญญาน Advanced Photo Systems : HDMI TO USB3.0 CONVERTER เปลี่ยนกล้องทุกตัวที่มี HDMI OUT ให้กลายเป็น WEBCAM ที่ได้ภาพคุณภาพสูงงง คมชัดถึง 1080P/60 แถมยังใช้ OTG Adapter ต่อใช้งานร่วมกับโทรศัพท์ Android ได้ด้วย (ผ่านแอพ CameraFi Live) หากกล้องมีการส่งสัญญานภาพและเสียงผ่านทาง HDMI ก็จะได้ภาพและเสียงพร้อมๆ กันจากตัวกล่อง ทันที</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.digital2home.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/ADVANCE-APS-HDMI-TO-USB3.0-CAPTURE-BOX-03.jpg.png\" style=\"height:159px; width:390px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>อุปกรณ์ในกล่อง : HDMI TO USB3.0 CONVERTER 1 ตัว / สาย USB 1 เส้น / คู่มือ 1 เล่ม</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>รุ่นกล้องที่ทดลองแล้วใช้งานได้</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>PANASONIC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GH5 ,GH4 ,G85 ,G7 ,GX8</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SONY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a5100 ,a6000 ,a6300 ,a6500,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A7 series</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Canon (มีเฉพาะภาพ ไม่มีเสียง)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>750D ,800D ,70D , 80D , 5DMK4</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NIKON (มีเฉพาะภาพ ไม่มีเสียง)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D600 ,D750, D800</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FUJI (มีเฉพาะภาพ ไม่มีเสียง)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>X-T2 ,X-T20</p>\r\n', '1012201615235fd2499b369b7.jpg', 6500, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 16:15:23', 0, '2020-12-10 16:15:23'),
(46, '', 'SONY PWS-110RX1 Network RX Station for XDCAM camcorders live streaming over 4G/LTE and Wi-Fi', 15, 52, '', 'Sony Network RX Station', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony Network RX Station for Select XDCAM Camcorders</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wireless solution offers high-quality live streaming at low cost</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The PWS-110RX1 network RX station is an advanced system for cost efficient live streaming video and audio direct from XDCAM camcorders using 4G/LTE and Wi-Fi networks. The PWS-110RX1 uses Sony&rsquo;s unique QoS (quality of service) technology or MPEG2-TS to maintain video and audio integrity during transmission. Each PWS-110RX1 unit can simultaneously control two SDI outputs: these can be used to live stream from two locations at the same time. Multiple systems can be added for greater input and output loads. The unit includes reference and timecode input connectors, which enable synchronised operation with broadcast systems. In addition, it can output in a variety of broadcast formats, including 1080i. The PWS-110RX1 system comes with preinstalled Connection Control Manager software that enables easy connection to camcorders and delivers efficient handling of the live streams. The system works with a 4G/LTE or Wi-Fi*1 dongle, or with the CBK-WA100 and CBK-WA101 wireless LAN adapter*2. The PXW-X180, PXW-X200 and PXW-X500 camcorders have built-in live streaming version upgrades*3. As well as live streaming, a planned upgrade will allow the unit to receive files transferred direct from camcorders.*4&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*1 CBK-WA02 wireless LAN adapter launch expected May 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*2 CBK-WA100 and CBK-WA101 firmware upgrade expected June 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*3 PXW-X180 upgrade scheduled for autumn 2015. PXW-X200 upgrade scheduled for June 2015. PXW-X500 upgrade scheduled for autumn 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*4 Requires version upgrade expected Autumn 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cost efficient live streaming of 1080i over 4G/LTE or Wi-Fi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Live streaming video and audio direct from XDCAM camcorders using 4G/LTE and Wi-Fi networks in a variety of broadcast formats, including 1080i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High quality Sony&#39;s QoS ensures no lost video or audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sony&rsquo;s unique QoS (quality of service) technology or MPEG2-TS to maintain video and audio integrity during transmission.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Direct streaming from XDCAM camcorders</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The system works with a 4G/LTE or Wi-Fi*1 dongle, or with the CBK-WA100 and CBK-WA101 Wireless Adapter*2. The PXW-X180, PXW-X200 and PXW-X500 have built-in live streaming version upgrades*3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*1 CBK-WA02 wireless LAN adapter launch expected May 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*2 CBK-WA100 and CBK-WA101 firmware upgrade expected June 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*3 PXW-X180 upgrade scheduled for autumn 2015. PXW-X200 upgrade scheduled for June 2015. PXW-X500 upgrade scheduled for autumn 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SDI outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Two SDI outputs on each unit allow you to manage two separate streams in and out. Multiple units can be used together to increase capacity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>PWS-110RX1A</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NETWORK RX Station Live Streaming over 4G/LTE &amp; WiFi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>อุปกรณ์รับสัญญาณวีดีโอผ่านเครื่อข่ายอินเตอร์เน็ตแบบ Live Streaming หรือ FTP โดยตรงจากกล้องวีดีโอตระกูล XDCAM สามารถใช้ได้กับกล้องดังต่อไปนี้</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- PXW-Z450 , PXW-X500 , PXW-X400</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- PXW-Z280 , PXW-Z190</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- PXW-Z150 , PXW-Z90, PXW-X70</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- CBK-WA100/101</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ตัวเครื่องใช้เทคโนโลยีการจัดการข้อมูลที่เรียกว่า SONY QoS Technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Real - Time ARQ (Automatic Repeat Request)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- ARC (Adaptive Rate Control)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FEC (Forword Error Correction)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รองรับวีดีโอ Live Streaming ทั้งแบบ H.264 และ H.265/HEVC และสามารถรับสัญญาณวีดีโอ Live Streaming ได้ถึง 30 กล้องในเวลาเดียวกัน&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ตัวเครื่อง PWS-110RX1A สามารถส่งภาพวีดีโอขาออกผ่านทางช่อง HD-SDI ได้จำนวน 2 ช่องสามารถตั้งค่าได้ดังนี้</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 1920 x 1080 : 59.94p , 59.94i ,50p ,50i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 1280 x 720 : 59.94p ,50p</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 720 x 576 : 50i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 720 x 480 : 59.94i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถตั้งค่าการรับ-ส่งวิดีโอ Live Streaming ได้ตั้งแต่ 0.5Mbps - 10Mbps&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Very High , High , Middle , Low , Very low</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถตั้งค่า Delay การรับส่งวีดีโอ Live streaming ได้ตั้งแต่ 1.5 วินาที - 10 วินาที</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Short&nbsp; 1.5 Sec</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Middle 3 sec&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Long 5 sec</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Very long 10 sec</p>\r\n\r\n<p>มีฟังก์ชั่น Intercom สามารถสื่อสารไปยังกล้องได้</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถแสดงแผนที่ปัจจุบันของกล้องได้ (GPS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถใช้รีโมทควบคุมการทำงานของกล้อง Zoom,Focus,Iris,WB,Rec ได้<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony PWS-110RX1A</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compatible Cameras PXW-Z450 / Z280 / Z190 / Z150 / Z90</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PXW-X500 / X400 / X200 / X180 / X70</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Formats 1080p: 59.94, 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080i: 59.94, 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720p: 59.94, 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>576i: 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>480i: 59.94</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectors 2 x RJ45, LAN Port (1000BASE-T, 100BASE-TX)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6 x USB 3.0 Type-A (2 Front and 4 Rear)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI 1.4a Type-A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x BNC, Ref Input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 x BNC, SDI Ports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x BNC, TC Input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory 2 x 8 GB SO-DIMM (DDR4)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage (SSD) 120 GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Expansion Bus Connector 2 x PCIe Gen2 8Lane (8 W)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU Intel Core i7 6700TE (2.4 GHz)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Requirements 100 to 240 VAC, 50/60 Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumption Normal: 235 W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Standby: 3 W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature 41 to 95&deg;F / 5 to 35&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage Temperature -4 to 140&deg;F / -20 to 60&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Humidity 20 to 90%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage Humidity 5 to 80%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 17.3 x 17.2 x 20.0&quot; / 44.0 x 43.6 x 50.7 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 21.6 lb / 9.8 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 29.15 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 25.75 x 22 x 7.75&quot;</p>\r\n', '1012201616475fd249ef0b87c.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 16:16:47', 0, '2020-12-10 16:16:47'),
(47, '', 'MOUNTING OPTIONS', 15, 51, '', 'Bird-Dog Encorder', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MOUNTING OPTIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>STUDIO NDI MOUNTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/6n/55/xh.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>V-MOUNT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This mounting option allows you neatly mount your Studio NDI between your V-Mount battery and your camera. The power pass through allows you to power your Studio NDI from your V-Mount battery via D-Tap and also pass power through to your camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/hh/i5/u7.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RACK</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Houses four Studio NDI in a 1RU space. Combined with dual encoding that enables eight encodes in 1 rack unit for the ultimate in high density NDI encoding.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/az/xs/x9.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAMERA MOUNT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the ultimate in flexibility for mounting on cameras, this mount gives an industry standard &frac14;-20 thread for attaching to ball heads, magic arms, and other standard camera mounting gear.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/a1/qu/f8.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MINI MOUNTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VESA MOUNT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>VESA Mount allows BirdDog Mini to be mounted behind any standard TV or Monitor. The perfect accessory when using Mini as an NDI playout decoder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/pu/za/ns.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAMERA MOUNT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the ultimate in flexibility for mounting on cameras, this mount gives an industry standard &frac14;-20 thread for attaching to ball heads, magic arms, and other standard camera mounting gear.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/a1/qu/f8.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TRIPOD MOUNT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Allows for easy mounting between a standard tripod plate and the bottom of the camera for neat and unobtrusive mounting applications.</p>\r\n', '1012201617465fd24a2a0c2ec.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 16:17:46', 0, '2020-12-10 16:17:46'),
(48, '', 'BIRD-DOG COMMS LIKE YOU\'VE NEVER SEEN BEFORE', 15, 51, '', 'Bird-Dog Encorder', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMMS LIKE YOU&#39;VE NEVER SEEN BEFORE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bird-Dog COMMS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>BIRDDOG HAVE REIMAGINED AUDIO INTERCOM FOR LIVE VIDEO PRODUCTIONS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By harnessing the true power of NDI, BirdDog Comms is the world&rsquo;s</p>\r\n\r\n<p>first audio intercom system integrating live camera feeds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be in total control and see every angle of your live production with live</p>\r\n\r\n<p>video windows from every BirdDog Studio enabled camera source.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TOUCH</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the fast paced world of live production, every second counts. By using a windows enabled touchscreen tablet the show director has complete lines of communication to the camera operators at their finger tips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PUSH TO TALK</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>BirdDog Comms fully supports Push To Talk (PTT) function. Simply push your call button on any BirdDog headset and talk to the group you have been set up in. It&rsquo;s really that easy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GROUPS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intuitive group management ensures everyone is on the right channel. BirdDog Comms makes it super easy to set up the call groups for clear lines of communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MORE INFORMATION ABOUT COMMS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>BirdDog Comms is the world&rsquo;s first audio visual comms system with full integration of all</p>\r\n\r\n<p>incoming camera video sources and crew talkback.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bird-Dog-2018-Second-image</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comms configuration and set up is so intuitive it&rsquo;s close to magic. Simply load the Comms application on your Windows 10 device, connect to the network and it just works. Comms runs on any Windows 10 device including touchscreen devices creating a truly tactile experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The large window preview can show any camera source or use it to monitor the program output from your NDI enabled switcher.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comms also supports AJA and Blackmagic devices allowing full quality output of the large video monitor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS COMMS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; BirdDog compatible NDI Encoder/Decoder</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Windows 10 and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Intel Core i5 series processor and above recommended</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Touch enabled device recommended</p>\r\n', '1012201620575fd24ae9cafdd.png', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 16:20:57', 0, '2020-12-10 16:20:57'),
(49, '', 'BIRD-DOG STUDIO NDI THE WORLD\'S BEST NDI ENCODER', 15, 51, '', 'Bird-Dog Encorder', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BIRD-DOG STUDIO NDI THE WORLD&#39;S BEST NDI ENCODER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CONNECT ANY CAMERA, COMPUTER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>OR CONSOLE TO ANY NETWORK</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bird-Dog Studio NDI</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>By connecting your video source to a BirdDog Studio NDI, your video becomes available anywhere on your network making connection to your favourite NDI production system a breeze.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Studio NDI is the world&rsquo;s most versatile, camera mountable, NDI encoder. With so many features packed into an aircraft grade aluminium case, Studio NDI gives you an unrivalled feature set.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PURE NDI</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Studio NDI is the world&rsquo;s only hardware based encoder supporting NDI at the full Bitrate. Broadcast quality. Ultra-low latency. iFrame codec. No compromises.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TALLY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Studio NDI makes Tally easy. Zero configuration, built-in large Tally display, selectable Tally borders on loop out, and an external Tally output.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CROSS CONVERSION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Studio NDI is the world&rsquo;s only NDI Encoder offering hardware based SDI to HDMI and HDMI to SDI cross conversion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FLEXIBLE POWER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Studio NDI can be powered by Power over Ethernet (PoE) or D-Tap from your camera battery. No need for a power adapter, although there is one in the box if you need it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LINK</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Link allows you to send NDI encoded from any BirdDog encoder and receive that NDI stream and decode on any BirdDog decoder. More compatible NDI sources will be added in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AUDIO COMMS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talk directly with camera operators using BirdDog Comms. Simply plug a headset in to Studio NDI and you are good to go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS STUDIO NDI&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video Formats</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; (HD) 1080p 23.98, 25, 29.97, 50, 59.94</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; (HD) 1080i 25, 29.97</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; (HD) 720p 50, 59.94</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; (SD) 525i, 625i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video Input</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 1 x 3G-SDI, SMPTE-259/292/296/424</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Level A / Level B)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 1 x HDMI Standard Type A connector</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI v1.4a, RGB or YCbCr<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video Output</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 1 x 3G-SDI, SMPTE-259/292/296/424 (Level A)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 1 x HDMI Standard Type A connector</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; HDMI v1.4a, RGB or YCbCr<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Audio Digital</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 2-Channel, 24-bit SDI embedded audio,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>48 kHz sample rate, synchronous</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 2-Channel, 24-bit HDMI embedded audio,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>48 kHz sample rate, synchronous<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Audio Analog</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 3.5mm Microphone headset input / output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Codec Support</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Realtime, ultra-low latency, full-bitrate NDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(i-frame)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Internal 35&times;5 bi-colour LED display for</p>\r\n\r\n<p>information and tally indication<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network Interface</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 10/100/1000 Ethernet (RJ-45) with PoE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Power over Ethernet)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Embedded web configuration panel for</p>\r\n\r\n<p>control and firmware updates<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>User Interface Controls</strong></p>\r\n\r