indows</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS : Windows 10 (64-bit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU 4th generation quad-core Intel i5 CPU (i5-4xxx or comparable)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB : USB 3.x port</p>\r\n', '1012201637495fd24edd756d6.jpg', 5290, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 16:37:49', 0, '2020-12-10 16:37:49');
