(86, '', 'Lumantek Ez-Pro 4k 18 CH. 12SDI 4k Video Switcher', 21, 62, '', 'Matrix Switcher', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Lumantek Ez-Pro 4k 18 CH. 12SDI 4k Video Switcher</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Feather</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Support 4k ULTRA HD&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>18 Chalnel 12-SDI</li>\r\n	<li>2 x Media Player , 2 x DSK</li>\r\n	<li>2 x Luma / Chroma&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>3 x Pattern</li>\r\n	<li><br />\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dz.lnwfile.com/_/dz/_raw/n6/d0/91.jpg\" style=\"height:704px; width:534px\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1012201845255fd26cc57073e.png', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:45:25', 0, '2020-12-10 18:45:25'),
(87, '', 'Lumantek EZ-PRO VS10 Full HD Video Switcher', 21, 62, '', 'Matrix Switcher', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-PRO VS10 Full HD Video Switcher</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>More Switcher for Everyone!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Again, LUMANTEK gives you another switcher good for live events but with more ports than before. More screens to monitor in a single switcher with a larger touch screen to control.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>User-Friendly LCD touch Screen</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our LCD touch screen and buttons make this switcher user-friendly.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can learn fast, and it is easy to control both video and sound.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal Scalers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ez-Pro VS10 comes with internal scalers in 4 input ports.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 AUX Outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You have plenty to show with 2 x SDI AUX ports. Enjoy more from ez-Pro VS10 while broadcasting.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Twice the Basic Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ez-Pro VS10 has 2 Picture in Picture (PIP) capabilities, 1 Still Image which covers the whole screen, and Luma and Chroma Keyer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ez-Pro VS10</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Input Ports</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8 x SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 pair x XLR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ez-Pro VS10</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Ports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x SDI (AUX 1 &amp; 2)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x SDI (Clean)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x SDI (Preview)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x SDI (Program)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI (Program)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI (Multiview)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 pair x XLR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ez-Pro VS10</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>10 INPUTS 1080P60 FULL HD VIDEO SWITCHER</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ITEM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connections</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 3G/HD/SD-SDI Input : BNC 75Ω 8ea (with Scaler)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; HDMI Input : 2ea (with Scaler)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 3G/HD/SD-SDI Output : BNC 75Ω 6ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; (AUX1/AUX2/AUX3/CLEAN/PGMx2)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; HDMI Output : 2ea (MULTIVIEW/PGM)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; TALLY: 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Reference Input: 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Ethernet: 1ea(1Gbps, RJ-45)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; USB2.0: 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; External Analog Audio Input : XLR 2ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; External Analog Audio Output : XLR 2ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; DC 12V: 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video Format Support</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 480i59/576i50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 1080p30/1080p29/1080p25/1080p24/1080p23</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 1080i60/1080i59/1080i50/720p60/720p59/720p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 1080p60/1080p59/1080p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video Switcher</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Mix &amp; Effect: 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; PIP: 2ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; KEY: 1ea(LUMA/CHROMA)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Downstream Keyer: 1ea(FILL/KEY)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Pattern Generator: 2ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Still Image: 2ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Multiview: 10view 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Audio Mixer: 10 stereo input mixer 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Management</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; TFT LCD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Physical</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Dimension: OO(H)XOO(W)XOO(D)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; (mm, Excluding Connector)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Weight: 00.00kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Environmental</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Operating Temperature: 0 ~ 45℃</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Requirement</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Power Input: DC 12V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Power Consumption: 00W(max)</p>\r\n', '1012201846045fd26cec8b13d.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:46:04', 0, '2020-12-10 18:46:04'),
(88, '', 'Lumantek ez-Pro VS4 4x1 Multiview Switcher for 3G-SDI and HDMI', 21, 62, '', 'Matrix Switcher', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek ez-Pro VS4 4x1 Multiview Switcher for 3G-SDI and HDMI&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>4-Input, 1-Channel HD Video</li>\r\n	<li>3G/HD/SD-SDI Inputs &amp; Outputs</li>\r\n	<li>Adjustable PiP, 2 x Logos, Luma Keyer</li>\r\n	<li>Embedded I/O &amp; External RCA Audio Input</li>\r\n	<li>Multiview Output through HDMI</li>\r\n	<li>Supports Level A &amp; Level B 3G-SDI</li>\r\n	<li>Wipe, Mix, Cut &amp; Additional Transitions</li>\r\n	<li>Embedded Audio Volume Control</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-PRO VS4 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The flexible ez-Pro VS4 4x1 Multiview Switcher from Lumantek is a standalone console switcher designed for corporate, educational, event, and house-of-worship applications. Integrated scaling enables you to mix and match up to four SD, HD, 3G-SDI, and HDMI signals. Program is output via HDMI or SDI, and a multiview display is available via HDMI. Features of the ez-Pro VS4 include an adjustable PiP (picture-in-picture) function, chroma/luma keying, embedded-audio volume control, and dual-logo insertion. Use the console buttons and T-bar to switch, cut, mix, wipe, and otherwise transition between sources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The compact ez-Pro VS4 switcher supports video resolutions up to Full HD 1080p60 with 8/10-bit 4:2:2 processing, and both Level A and Level B 3G-SDI transmission. Up to four channels of embedded audio are supported, plus external audio via stereo RCA inputs. An integrated USB 2.0 interface is provided for firmware upgrades, logo input, and a GUI application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mix and match 3G/HD/SD-SDI and HDMI sources</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports up to 1080p60 HD video</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multiview output via HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Automatic scaling</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PiP function with adjustable position and size</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Incorporates up to two logos</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chroma and luma key functions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Volume control for embedded audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>External audio input via stereo RCA jacks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diverse transition effects</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-PRO VS4 Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Input 1 x SDI/HDMI selective</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x SDI (BNC, 75 Ohms)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio Input 2 x 1/4&quot; stereo RCA jacks (balanced, &plusmn;10 V max at -10 dB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Output Program:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x SDI (BNC, 75 Ohms)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multiview:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio Output 1 x 3.5 mm stereo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Input Resolutions SD:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>480i: 50/59</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p: 30/29.97/25/24/23.98</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080i: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720p: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Output Resolutions HD:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p: 30/29.97/25/24/23.98</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080i: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720p: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB Interface USB 2.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Input 7-14 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumption (Maximum) 20 W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature 32 to 104&deg;F / 0 to 40&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 2.8 x 11.7 x 9.1&quot; / 70 x 297 x 230 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 3.7 lb / 1.7 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 5.25 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 13.937 x 10.236 x 4.488&quot;</p>\r\n', '1012201846455fd26d157fbb4.jpg', 39000, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:46:45', 0, '2020-12-10 18:46:45');
