(89, '', 'Lumantek EZ-PRO VM6 6x4 HD-SDI Matrix Switcher', 21, 62, '', 'Matrix Switcher', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-PRO VM6 6x4 HD-SDI Matrix Switcher</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Lumantek EZ-PRO VM6 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 6x4 HD-SDI Matrix Switcher from Lumantek is an all-in-one matrix switcher that supports live switching of media or cameras with 6 x SD/HD-SDI inputs and 4 x SD/HD-SDI outputs. The switcher first output A has two BNC connector ports, and an additional BNC port 7 provides Fill/Key input with selected license option.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It features frame sync on each input, on-board control panel, and supports remote control via an optional console controller. The switcher is equipped with 10-bit processing and analog audio embedding with 2 x stereo XLR inputs. All video/audio channels are controlled separately. One HDMI preview channel allows the display of six video source inputs with two other background channels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hybrid between video matrix and switcher</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simultaneous multi-channel switching supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported resolutions: 1080i 60/59.94/50, 720p 60/59.94/50, 625i, 525i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported HDMI output resolutions: 1080p 60/50, 720p 60/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Auxiliary output supported for the Presenter view</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Preview mode: HDMI 1080p, 720p, 576p, 480p</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Optional fill and key system</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Black console included (connected through Ethernet cable)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-PRO VM6 Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Input 6 x BNC 75 Ohms, SD/HD-SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x BNC 75 Ohms, Fill/Key (port 7)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio Input 2 x XLR, stereo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Output 4 x BNC 75 Ohms, HD-SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x BNC 75 Ohms, HD-SDI (port A)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multiview Outputs 1 x HDMI, (1080p at 60/50, 720p at 60/50, 576p at 50, 487p at 60)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Controls</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Control Buttons At Front:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6 x input select</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 x output select</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LCD At Front:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Status and control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LED Indicator Large &#39;L&#39; logo LED at front to identify device status</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB Rear: Easy to use GUI application (Firmware update)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>General</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal Processing 4:2:2 10-bit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution Supported 1920 x 1080i at 59.94/60/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1280 x 720p at 59.94/60/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720 x 576i at 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720 x 487i at 59.94</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Input 115 to 240 VAC at 50/60 Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumption 30 W maximum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operation Temperature 32 to 104&deg;F / 0 to 40&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 1.7 x 19 x 9.4&quot; / 44 x 483 x 240 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 6.8 lb / 3.1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/8i/z9/hf.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '1012201847145fd26d326135b.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:47:14', 0, '2020-12-10 18:47:14'),
(90, '', 'Lumantek ez-CGER mini Live HD-SDI USB Fill/Key and CG Generator with CGER Software', 21, 63, '', 'CG Generetor', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek ez-CGER mini Live HD-SDI USB Fill/Key and CG Generator with CGER Software</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB 3.0 Input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fill/Key SDI Outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Resolution up to 1080i60</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No Power Connection Needed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-CGER MINI Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ez-CGER mini Live HD-SDI USB Fill/Key and CG Generator from Lumantek is a simple and small HD live graphic system for live conferences and active video presentations. Create and present on-screen CG and texts in real-time using the generator and CGER software via the USB 3.0 port, and generate Fill/Key signals to the HD-SDI port.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Complimentary ez-CGER CG software for Windows OS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>User friendly interface</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Insert texts, images, sequences, videos, and widgets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mini converter type</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No power connection needed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-CGER MINI Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input 1 x USB 3.0, Fill/Key port</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output 1 x BNC, HD-SDI Fill&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x BNC, HD-SDI Key</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB Device Support USB 3.0 Video Streamer Device: Fill &amp; Key input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB 2.0 to Serial (COM Port) Device: Control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB 2.0 to SPI Device: Firmware update</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal Video Processing YCbCr 4:2:2 10-bit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Resolution 1280 x 720p: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920 x 1080i: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Image Formats JPG, PNG, BMP, GIF, and TGA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Video Formats WMV, AVI, and MP4</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Management USB: Easy to use GUI application, Firmware update</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature 32 to 104&deg;F / 0 to 40&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (H x L) 3 x 4.5&quot; / 76 x 115 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight Not specified by manufacturer<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Packaging Info</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 1.2 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 8.2 x 6.0 x 3.7&quot;</p>\r\n', '1012201848435fd26d8bbe59b.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:48:43', 0, '2020-12-10 18:48:43'),
(91, '', 'Lumantek ez-DSK Live CG Generator Four SDI & One HDMI Outputs', 21, 63, '', 'CG Generetor', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Lumantek ez-DSK Live CG Generator Four SDI &amp; One HDMI Outputs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One SDI Input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Four SDI &amp; One HDMI Outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reclocked Outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>User Friendly Interface</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easy Connection Through USB 3.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-DSK Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ez-DSK Live CG Generator from Lumantek allows easy application of computer graphics like subtitles, images, sequences, videos, and widgets into your outgoing video source. This distributor/converter features an SDI video input with loop-output, four SDI outputs, and a CG input USB 3.0 port. The overlay method of ez-DSK doesn&#39;t take any extra video ports like conventional Fill/Key generators and allows zero delay transmission. It is equipped with fail-safe trigger mechanism to prevent any disruption if any malfunction occurs. All outgoing ports reclock the video source for better quality video. The ez-DSK works as a distributor and a converter by distributing the outgoing source into four BNC SDI outputs and an HDMI port. The ez-CGER dedicated complimentary software lets you create and overlay CG graphics, add images, videos, sequences, and texts to your video source.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easy connection through USB 3.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reclocked Outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Complimentary CG software &quot;ez-CGER&quot; for Windows OS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>User friendly interface</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fail-safe mechanism</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek EZ-DSK Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inputs 1 x BNC 75 Ohms, SDI video&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SD: 480i59 and 576i50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD: 1080p30, 1080p29, 1080p25, 1080p24, 1080p23, 1080i60, 1080i59, 1080i50, 720p60, 720p59, and 720p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD: 1080p60, 1080p59, and 1080p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x USB 3.0, CG input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD: 1080p30, 1080p29, 1080p25, 1080i60, 1080i59, 1080i50, 720p60, 720p59, and 720p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Outputs 4 x BNC 75 Ohms, SDI video&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SD: 480i59 and 576i50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD: 1080p30, 1080p29, 1080p25, 1080p24, 1080p23, 1080i60, 1080i59, 1080i50, 720p60, 720p59, and 720p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD: 1080p60, 1080p59, and 1080p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x BNC 75 OHms , SDI loop&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SD: 480i59 and 576i50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD: 1080p30, 1080p29, 1080p25, 1080p24, 1080p23, 1080i60, 1080i59, 1080i50, 720p60, 720p59, and 720p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD: 1080p60, 1080p59, and 1080p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI 75 Ohms</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SD: 480i59 and 576i50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD: 1080p30, 1080p29, 1080p25, 1080p24, 1080p23, 1080i60, 1080i59, 1080i50, 720p60, 720p59, and 720p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD: 1080p60, 1080p59, and 1080p50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Control 1 x USB 3.0 Type-B, CG port</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumption 7 W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input Power 7 to 18 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature 32 to 104&deg;F / 0 to 40&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 1.7 x 5.5 x 4.7&quot; / 4.4 x 14.0 x 11.9 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 17.6 oz / 0.5 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 2.35 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 7.6 x 5.7 x 4.5&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1012201849165fd26dac33c4f.jpg', 81000, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:49:16', 0, '2020-12-10 18:49:16'),
(92, '', 'Lumantek EZ-CGER VM4 HD Switcher & Graphic Mixer', 21, 63, '', 'CG Generetor', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;Lumantek EZ-CGER VM4 HD Switcher &amp; Graphic Mixer</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Lumantek EZ-CGER VM4 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ez-CGER HD Switcher &amp; Graphic Mixer from Lumantek includes the ez-CGER hybrid system and the ez-LiveSurface control surface. The ez-CGER is comprised of CG software and a video switcher. It communicates with the CG software for system control, and can be connected to a PC through USB 3.0 ports. The system supports up to six media input sources via four HD-SDI and two HDMI ports. The CG is mixed with the input sources by software via USB 3.0 and transmitted through HD-SDI/HDMI/VGA outputs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The system also features one each SDI, HDMI, and VGA output ports for transmitting signals with various resolutions. The multiview output enables users to monitor up to four live input sources, as well as PiP. The ez-CGER system supports HDMI/SDI embedded audio or XLR external audio. In addition, SDI or HDMI input audio inputs are synchronized with the video and can be switched seamlessly without generating any noise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>File play input for CG software</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD level input and output resolution support</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Various HDMI/VGA output resolution support with the scaler</p>\r\n\r\n<p>User-friendly interface</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Insert texts, images, sequences, videos, and widgets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Black console included (connected through Ethernet cable)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lumantek EZ-CGER VM4 Specs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inputs Video:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x HD-SDI or HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x HD-SDI only</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fill &amp; Key Input:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x USB 3.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x XLR, stereo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x File input (various formats)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Outputs Video:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Scaled Video:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x VGA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multiview (4x1):</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x USB 3.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB USB 3.0 Video Streamer Device: Fill and key input, multiview output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB 2.0 USB to Serial (COM Port) Device: Control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB 2.0 USB to SPI Device: Firmware update</p>\r\n\r\n<p>System Requirements OS: Windows 7, Windows 8, 32-bit/64-bit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU: Intel i5 2.8 GHz and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB 3.0 host controller</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For Software Installation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS: Windows 7 or higher version</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU: 4th generation intel i7 or above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RAM: 8 GB or above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphics: GeForce GTX 750 or above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Monitor Resolution: 1920 x 1080 or above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB 3.0 port</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal Video Processing Video Switcher: YCbCr 4:2:2 10-bit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fill &amp; Key Input: RGBA 4:4:4:4 8-bit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multiview Output: YCbCr 4:2:2 8-bit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution Supported 1080p 60/59.94/50 (converted to 1080i automatically)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080i 60/59.94/50/30/29.97/25</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720p 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Management Device status LED (front)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB for GUI application, firmware update (rear)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumption 30 W maximum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature 32 to 104&deg;F / 0 to 40&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (H x W x D) 1.73 x 19 x 9.4&quot; / 4.4 x 48.3 x 24.0 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 6.8 lb / 3.1 kg</p>\r\n', '1012201849495fd26dcd37b72.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:49:49', 0, '2020-12-10 18:49:49'),
(93, '', 'LUMANTEK EZ-HS + CONVERTER-SCALER', 21, 64, '', 'Converter', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย LUMANTEK&nbsp; EZ-HS +&nbsp; CONVERTER-SCALER</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>LUMANTEK Scaler ez-Converters are converters with many more options to facilitate video transfer. By managing the &quot;dip switch&quot;, the user will be able to change the video resolution from 480i to 1080p60. There are two models of Scaler ez-converters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Video Input Format:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VGA&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>640 &times; 480&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>800 &times; 600&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1024 &times; 768&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1280 &times; 1024&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1600 &times; 1200&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920 &times; 1080&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720x480i@59.94/60, 720x576i @ 50&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1280x720p @ 50, 1280x720p@59.94/60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920x1080i @ 50, 1920x1080i@59.94 / 60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920x1080i@23.94/24, 1920x1080p @ 25, 1920x1080p@29.97/30&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920x1080p @ 50, 1920x1080p@59.94/60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Video Output format:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720x480i @ 59.94 / 60, 720x576i @ 50&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1280x720p @ 50, 1280x720p @ 59.94 / 60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920x1080i @ 50, 1920x1080i @ 59.94 / 60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920x1080p@23.94/24, 1920x1080p @ 25, 1920x 1080p@29.97/30&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1920x1080p @ 50, 1920x1080p@59.94/60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Video Aspect Ratio: Full / Center cut / Letter Box / 14: 9 Center cut</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Audio Input Connector: 3.5mm stereo Jack x 1&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Video Input Connector:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI (Type A) x1&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VGA x 1&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Video Output Connector: BNC x 1&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC Input Power: 5V ~ 18V&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1012201851395fd26e3ba6965.png', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:51:39', 0, '2020-